ext":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","bangl_text":"সে সুখীজীবন যাপন করবে।","english_text":"He will be in a pleasant life","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/101007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","bangl_text":"আর যার পাল্লা হালকা হবে","english_text":"But as for one whose scales are light","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/101008.mp3"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","bangl_text":"তার ঠিকানা হবে হাবিয়া।","english_text":"His refuge will be an abyss","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/101009.mp3"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","bangl_text":"আপনি জানেন তা কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what that is","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/101010.mp3"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","bangl_text":"প্রজ্জ্বলিত অগ্নি","english_text":"It is a Fire, intensely hot","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/101011.mp3"}]}}